title: Michelle Wolf And Amber Ruffin: Late Night Trivia Fight
description: Michelle Wolf talks about her performance at the White House Correspondents' dinner. Amber Ruffin chats about writing for Late Night With Seth Meyers. This episode originally aired Nov. 30, 2018.
